red by the market rule. The Q‑code indicates an aerodrome‑level notice, not a FIR closure, so the proposition’s definition of a major non‑weather closure is not satisfied. Accordingly, the preponderance of the record does not demonstrate the required closure.\"}","tool":"aar_submit_council_vote"},"id":"chatcmpl-tool-a71282a88d8ab9cf","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"openai/gpt-oss-120b","provider":"openrouter","responseId":"gen-1781906958-1fSrRBeMwwDI6kMMmPr1","role":"assistant","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781906958590,"usage":{"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"input":0,"output":0,"total":0},"input":19918,"output":420,"totalTokens":20402}},"type":"thinking_end"},"message":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"reasoning","type":"thinking"},{"arguments":{"args":"{\"vote\":\"not_demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted NOTAM A1010/26 only closes airports in the western Tehran FIR and suspends permissions, without evidence of a broad airspace or transiting flight closure required by the market rule. The Q‑code indicates an aerodrome‑level notice, not a FIR closure, so the proposition’s definition of a major non‑weather closure is not satisfied. Accordingly, the preponderance of the record does not demonstrate the required closure.\"}","tool":"aar_submit_council_vote"},"id":"chatcmpl-tool-a71282a88d8ab9cf","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"openai/gpt-oss-120b","provider":"openrouter","responseId":"gen-1781906958-1fSrRBeMwwDI6kMMmPr1","role":"assistant","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781906958590,"usage":{"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"input":0,"output":0,"total":0},"input":19918,"output":420,"totalTokens":20402}},"type":"message_update"}
